      "text": "Hourly Load Data Archives\n\n- Hourly Load Data Archives\n- Load\n- Grid Information\n- Home\n\n# Hourly Load Data Archives\n\nHistorical information on hourly loads by ERCOT control area is provided for the years 1995-2016, with the exception of 2001, for which there is no available data.\n\nThe information may vary from report to report. Since April 2003, ERCOT has reported on load data in its eight weather zones. Prior to April 2003, ERCOT was divided into 11 control areas, and the load data was reported accordingly.\n\nReport Availability: The Hourly Load Archive report for the previous month is typically available around the 9th of the current month, to allow for settlements to process.\n\n## Key Documents\n\n2026 ERCOT Hourly Load Data\n\nMar 11, 2026 - zip - 174.7 KB\n\n2025 ERCOT Hourly Load Data\n\nFeb 4, 2026 - zip - 1 MB\n\n2024 ERCOT Hourly Load Data\n\nJan 10, 2025 - zip - 1 MB\n\n2023 ERCOT Hourly Load Data\n\nJan 8, 2024 - zip - 1 MB\n\n2022 ERCOT Hourly Load Data\n\nJan 31, 2023 - zip - 1 MB\n\n2021 ERCOT ",
